otherFacts.value: Separate Room, In House, With Storage

data.description: This dream home has the most amazing peaceful views of the mountains and the train as it slowly passes by. 3 car garage, large lot, 4 bedrooms, 2 1/2 bathrooms, indoor laundry room with storage and quartz counters, large living room with tray ceiling, stunning wood looking tile floors & a large open floor plan. Check out the kitchen with the large quartz island, beautiful backsplash, stainless steel appliances, stainless steel sink with great mountain views. Huge master with large walk-in closet, the master bathroom is made to impress with large walk in shower!...full tile, rain overhead showerhead in a thick glass enclosure. Patio and much more!
